24.03	Connie_Nielsen	Connie Nielsen	Connie Inge-Lise Nielsen (born 3 July 1965) is a Danish actress. She is known for her roles in the English language films Gladiator, The Devil's Advocate, Basic, and The Ice Harvest. She currently stars as Meredith Kane on the Starz series Boss.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/e/ec/ConnieNielsen09TIFF.jpg/220px-ConnieNielsen09TIFF.jpg
